{"tid":1254640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有市民向法庭申請禁制令　要求禁止無展示編號警員執勤","createTime":"2019-06-24T08:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:40:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":353,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"172f1d1cf6575aa512666da0467bb78ac6f46267","tid":1254640,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:25:46.000Z","msg":"有市民準備入稟高等法院，就6月12日特別戰術小隊沒有顯示警員編號執勤申請司法覆核，並申請禁制令禁止沒有展示警員編號的警員執勤。<br />\n<br />\n申請人陳先生說，當晚他在夏慤道一個公園休息時，看見沒有展示警員編號的速龍小隊迎面而來，於是取出手機拍攝，卻遭速龍小隊威嚇他收起手機。<br />\n<br />\n他說，香港是法治社會，應可自由拍攝，對於警員阻止他拍攝感到不解，但速龍小隊的制服沒有顯示警員編號，無法投訴及展開訴訟，因此通過法庭、法律爭取公平和公義。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生說，如速龍小隊的制服有編號，便可直接向警方投訴，但如今沒有編號，只能循監警會投訴，惟監警會處理投訴的時間十分漫長，投訴也沒有意思。<br />\n<br />\n對於保安局局長李家超早前指，速龍小隊的制服沒有位置可以展示警員編號，陳先生指是推卸責任。"},{"pid":"b9f9b0038e8e28e49ff7a311cbf574225f6b6928","tid":1254640,"uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:25:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464712-20190624.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464712-20190624.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=54102b77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464712-20190624.htm&h=45a481e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464712-20190624.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5ed87270e71c07967a1a229c221957794d7c1001","tid":1254640,"uid":202730,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:25:58.000Z","msg":"急 召日本巴絲或者用開twitter巴絲<br />\n可以推廣到去日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做好文宣<br />\n<br />\n粵語<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Iwxt5qH2Vto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIwxt5qH2Vto&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVB1